628
00:50:48.504 --> 00:50:51.047
We're gonna go home.
and everything's gonna be good.

629
00:50:51.131 --> 00:50:52.382
It's gonna be all right.

630
00:50:56.720 --> 00:50:57.720
Okay.

631
