688
01:00:45.517 --> 01:00:48.018
If someone sees you. we both will die.

689
01:00:48.812 --> 01:00:50.479
Coming back here is so dangerous.

690
01:00:51.606 --> 01:00:53.899
- Did you find her?
- She's dead.

691
01:00:57.654 --> 01:00:58.988
Oh. I'm...

692
